games.comment: Shonn Greene accomplished: Jones compiled 121 yards and a score on 26 carries, while Greene managed 144 yards and 2 touchdowns on 19 attempts. One may think that Greene got a bunch of touches late when the game was out of hand, but 9 of his 19 rushes came in the second quarter.
Shonn Greene handled most of the workload, gaining 94 yards on 11 carries, though most of it came on a 52-yard burst.
